### Login para obter dados do usuário autenticadado
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/me HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Login para deslogar do sistema
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/logout HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

